  "name": "Wraithguard Cloak",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<img src=\"Art%20-%20Items/cloaks/cloak_black_white_wraithguard.webp\" /><p>This cloak, once worn by a veteran of the Shining Crusade, now grants enhanced resistance against deathly magic. In addition to providing +3 to all saving throws, the mantle can activate a <em>death ward</em> effect once per day, granting the wearer temporary immunity to death effects, negative energy, and energy drain for 9 minutes. This ancient relic was lost during a doomed stand against Tar-Baphon's undead legions.</p><p>Death Ward:<br /><span style=\"font-family:ALBR55X, 'Font Awesome 5 Free'\">The subject gains a +4 morale bonus on saves against all death spells and magical death effects. The subject is granted a save to negate such effects even if one is not normally allowed. The subject is immune to energy drain and any negative energy effects, including channeled negative energy.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-color:initial;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:ALBR55X, 'Font Awesome 5 Free';font-size:14.625px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:ALBR55X, 'Font Awesome 5 Free'\">This spell does not remove negative levels that the subject has already gained, but it does remove the penalties from negative levels for the duration of its effect.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-color:initial;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:ALBR55X, 'Font Awesome 5 Free';font-size:14.625px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:ALBR55X, 'Font Awesome 5 Free'\"><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-color:initial\">Death ward</em> does not protect against other sorts of attacks, even if those attacks might be lethal.</span></p>",
